data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a highly desirable area! This charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch-style residence is nestled on a picturesque one-acre lot surrounded by the tranquil beauty of a creek. Step inside to discover a beautiful interior with a spacious living area that welcomes you with warmth and natural light, creating the perfect atmosphere for relaxation or entertaining guests. The heart of the home is the stylish kitchen, featuring modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient walk-in pantry for all your storage needs. Adjacent to the kitchen is a versatile space that was once a garage but has been tastefully finished to provide additional living space, offering endless possibilities for use as a home office, gym, or media room. Retreat to the comfortable bedrooms, including a serene master suite complete with its own private bathroom for added convenience. With two additional bedrooms, there's plenty of room for family, guests, or a home office. Outside, the expansive backyard offers endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. This home is being sold as is, with the assurance of a new roof, new subflooring, new floors, and more, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Don't miss your chance to own this truly exceptional property in a great location. Schedule your showing today and make this your forever home!  Preferred Lender Homeowners Financial Group Casey Simmons
